Destroy a condition variable.

== Syntax ==

<syntaxhighlight lang='c'>
void SDL_DestroyCond(SDL_cond * cond);
</syntaxhighlight>

== Function Parameters ==

{|
|'''cond'''
|the condition variable to destroy
|}

== Version ==

This function is available since SDL 3.0.0.

